cs.DC, cs.DB, cs.NI, cs.CR, cs.SY

This paper is about evaluating and comparing the performance of Hadoop clusters using a standardized Big Data benchmark. The focus is on the network setup and its influence on the performance. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing). Other likely sub-categories include cs.DB (Databases), cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
